# MatchMate ğŸ‘¥ğŸ’

**MatchMate** is a matrimonial-style Android app that allows users to swipe through match cards, accept or decline matches, and persist those decisions even offline.

---

## ğŸš€ Features

- ğŸ§  MVVM architecture using ViewModel, LiveData, Repository
- ğŸŒ Fetch user profiles from [randomuser.me](https://randomuser.me/)
- ğŸ“¦ Persist match decisions using Room DB (offline support)
- ğŸ–¼ï¸ Load profile pictures using Glide
- ğŸ”„ Retrofit for API integration
- ğŸ“± Clean UI with RecyclerView + ViewBinding

---

## ğŸ—ï¸ Tech Stack

| Layer          | Tool/Library                          |
|----------------|---------------------------------------|
| UI             | RecyclerView, ConstraintLayout, ViewBinding |
| Network        | Retrofit + Gson                       |
| Image Loading  | Glide                                 |
| Local DB       | Room                                  |
| Architecture   | MVVM (ViewModel, Repository, LiveData)|
